We're sorry about the power cut in the area. The power cut is affecting 145 properties in the area shown on the map. We are working with our engineers to fix the problem as quickly as possible, and will keep you updated here on Power Track.

Engineers have arrived in the area. They are working hard to fix the problem and will get your power back on as quickly as possible. At this stage, we're aiming to have your power back on by 15:00 03/10/2025. If this changes, we'll let you know.

If you need more information, please send us a message on Whatsapp or call us on 105 and quote reference 'RU7141'
